precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign the AGREEMENT
FOR THE AFFILIATION OF THE INTERNATIONAL CENTRE FOR CRIMINAL LAW REFORM
AND CRIMINAL JUSTICE POLICY with the UNITED NATIONS, or (b) to issue an
Instrument of Full Powers authorizing Peter Walker or Philip MacKinnon to
sign the said agreement.
